"To safely and seamlessly integrate externally funded projects into the railway environment, whilst minimising impacts on railway operations and operational infrastructure. Leverage knowledge and understanding of rail related risks and constraints to facilitate solutions that align with the external client objectives whilst meeting all stakeholder requirements. To provide guidance to the external client team to support adherence to relevant Network Rail and rail industry standards and processes. Ideally have a good understanding of risk assessment in relation to construction methods and a good understanding and appreciation of construction programmes for estimating durations and forecasts in appreciation of customer proposals. Ability to appreciate construction drawings and be a good communicator to facilitate and aid the customer for the delivery of their work proposals."